    "en": {
      "title": "Key meeting today for egg producers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The All Sri Lankan Egg Producers Association has informed that they will discuss with the Commerce Minister today (22) regarding the fixing of the maximum retail price for eggs.",
        "The consumer authority has recently issued a gazette fixing the maximum retail price of 43 rupees per white egg and 45 rupees per red egg.",
        "However, it is noteworthy that the All Sri Lankan Egg Producers Association has requested that the said gazette notification be canceled and steps should be taken to fix the price so as to cover the costs. (a)"
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "today",
          "label": "DATE"
        }
      ],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
            "text": "The All Sri Lankan Egg Producers Association",
            "label": "WORK_OF_ART"
          },
